{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127347488487903232367089.jpeg/XuuLzwOn92xfdbXUUIKO6HC-m_SGIiVDR2EGJkdhBiY\" alt=\"陳欣茵節目係咁樣。（截圖）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵節目係咁樣。（截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127347490778124288710463.jpeg/tQo8cXT6OJS0pQv6UDzUPtCJVH3UnlXS52jRFOdo0RQ\" alt=\"陳欣茵平時的IG相。（ig圖片）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵平時的IG相。（ig圖片）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127347970040139776026815.jpeg/87YmF9T77NJaBQSBbQzS_0rK__TOvObGCrxBWwq8QVs\" alt=\"陳欣茵身材比例，只可以用嬌小有睇頭形容。（截圖）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵身材比例，只可以用嬌小有睇頭形容。（截圖）</figcaption></figure><p>152cm嬌小身形離奇「增高」</p><p>眾所周知，陳欣茵一向走嬌小玲瓏路線，身高約152cm的她，雖然上圍出眾，但就不時被網民搞笑指是「短腿」一族。豈料在最新的生日帖文中，陳欣茵疑似太想展現完美體態，修圖「重手咗」，又或是配合了極致的「低炒」神級攝影角度，令原本152cm的身高離奇地「極速發育」！</p><p>有網民留言：「真係以為係有180」、「P到呢」，看來大家都有相同感覺？</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348040030621696278493.jpeg/K7r0GEoKviY-c35jBWQghe7qd390CLoV8hqrU_Iaq1M\" alt=\"陳欣茵？真係你？（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵？真係你？（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348037094477824824079.jpeg/pCjicLwESLw9jRSPqylDUT3-fOXzm3RlZCVczGQlXMw\" alt=\"陳欣茵「高」咗咁多。（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵「高」咗咁多。（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348116396576768406189.jpeg/mNWM60ZLojBcAolRqQoZQa4FP4qaB8O1C7J40wuyeNM\" alt=\"陳欣茵「高」咗咁多。（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵「高」咗咁多。（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348114248962048723095.jpeg/LiN6qV1WLik_Uf9tDtRXcFkyDj7Wg8NO7IJaO-yCWjs\" alt=\"勉強認到五官係陳欣茵。（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>勉強認到五官係陳欣茵。（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348111941963776413295.jpeg/PFOTNSJX5lICE62r08K_RfbDDqdEnGAiR9LD5EfSw-Q\" alt=\"勉強認到五官係陳欣茵。（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>勉強認到五官係陳欣茵。（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127348109446221824243175.jpeg/wl7R8EiOCDbOikreQgzJ__FparesxzR6ftL0b37S9G8\" alt=\"陳欣茵「P圖」會唔會太重手？（ig@yanyaascyy）\"><figcaption>陳欣茵「P圖」會唔會太重手？（ig@yanyaascyy）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T12:10:23.108052+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":397,"images":9,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}